description: The fund is considered a “fund of funds” that, under normal market conditions, seeks to achieve its investment objective by principally investing in unaffiliated international equity ETFs. The fund will attempt to exceed returns of the MSCI ACWI ex USA Index by overweighting and underweighting its exposure to geographic locations relative to the index and may also invest in geographic regions not represented in the index. It is non-diversified.
name: Day Hagan/Ned Davis Research Smart Sector International ETF
